name: Camacho - 10th Anniversary - 6 x 60
additionalNotes: The Camacho 10th Anniversary is a special box pressed Corojo Puro, using 100% Honduran Corojo tobacco, commemorating the 10th anniversary of The Camacho family growing the first worlds truly authentic corojo tobacco. This medium to full bodied cigar is highly flavorful using the master blending techniques Camacho is known for to create this enjoyable smoke.
